{"sn2.15:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.15 ","sn2.15:0.2":"2. Anathapindikavagga ","sn2.15:0.3":"Candanasutta ","sn2.15:1.1":"Ekamantam thito kho candano devaputto bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn2.15:2.1":"“Kathamsu tarati ogham, ","sn2.15:2.2":"rattindivamatandito; ","sn2.15:2.3":"Appatitthe analambe, ","sn2.15:2.4":"ko gambhire na sidati”ti. ","sn2.15:3.1":"“Sabbada silasampanno, ","sn2.15:3.2":"Pannava susamahito; ","sn2.15:3.3":"Araddhaviriyo pahitatto, ","sn2.15:3.4":"Ogham tarati duttaram. ","sn2.15:4.1":"Virato kamasannaya, ","sn2.15:4.2":"rupasamyojanatigo; ","sn2.15:4.3":"Nandiragaparikkhino, ","sn2.15:4.4":"so gambhire na sidati”ti. "}